## Description
Redhat Kernel RDMA QE Python libs and tests.

## Installation

```console
$ dnf install -y python3-pip.noarch
$ pip3 install --user python-rdma-qe
```
## Upgrade
```console
$ pip3 list | grep python-rdma-qe
$ pip3 install -U python-rdma-qe
```
## Uninstallation
```console
$ pip3 uninstall python-rdma-qe
```
## Usage
```console
$ python3
